<div class="container-fluid container-main">
  <div class="row hidden-xs-down" style="border-bottom: solid 2px #D92329;">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3 no-gutter">
      <%= image_tag 'better_days_sandwich.jpg', class: "img-responsive" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3 no-gutter">
      <%= image_tag 'better_days_salad.jpg', class: "img-responsive" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3 no-gutter">
      <%= image_tag 'smoked-spare-rib.jpg', class: "img-responsive" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-3 no-gutter">
      <%= image_tag 'smoked_chicken_wings.jpg', class: "img-responsive" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row p-t-2">

      <div class="col-md-9">
        <div class="jumbotron">
          <h1>Better Days BBQ - Smyrna, TN</h1>
          <p>We specialize in mouth-watering slow-smoked barbecue at prices that cannot be beat! Established in 2015, Better Days BBQ is quickly becoming the go-to spot for takeout BBQ done right, every time, in Smyrna, Tennessee. </p>
          <p><b>Better BBQ</b> at <b>Better Prices</b> means <b>Better Days!</b></p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="p-t-3" style="color: #000;">Recent News / Events</h2>

        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
          <article class="row p-b-2">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
              <h3><%= link_to post.title, post_path(post), class: "" %></h3>
              <div><%= post.content.html_safe %></div>
              <div class="pull-right"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> <%= post.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></div>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% end %>
        <div><%= link_to "See All News / Events / Posts", posts_path %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2> (615) 713-6039</h2>
        <p>11469 Old Nashville Hwy<br>Smyrna, TN 37167</p>
        <h2>Current Specials</h2>
        <p>Better Half-Pound Pulled Pork Sandwich - $4</p>
        <h2>Party Orders and Events</h2>
        <p>Let us provide the food for your next event or party. Give us a call, (615) 713-6039, or <a href="mailto:">send us an email</a> for pricing or to learn more.</p>
